These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-1::.
There are 7 different nationalities: indian, malaysian, chinese, indonesian, japanese, colombian, argentine
1. the malaysian is in the middle##1
2. the malaysian is on the left of the chinese##1
3. the japanese is on the right of the indonesian##1
4. the indian is on the right of the chinese##1
5. the argentine is on the far left##1
6. the colombian is on the right of the indian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |    4     |   5    |   6   |    7     |
| Nationality   | argentine | indonesian | japanese | malaysian | chinese | indian | colombian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-2::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  electrician, photographer, engineer, architect, scientist, coach, dressmaker
1. the dressmaker is on the far right##1
2. the electrician is on the far left##1
3. the electrician is on the left of the scientist##1
4. the scientist is on the left of the engineer##1
5. the architect is on the right of the coach##1
6. the dressmaker is on the right of the photographer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |    2    |      3       |   4   |     5     |   6    |    7    |
| Job   | electrician | scientist | engineer | coach | architect | photographer | dressmaker |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-3::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: cooking, baking, gardening, collecting, hiking, reading, video-games
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is in the middle##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far right##1
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
6. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2      |   3    |    4    |      5      |     6      |    7    |
| Hobby   | hiking | cooking | reading | gardening | video-games | baking | collecting |

 #################################

 
