3. the person eating kiwi is on the far left##1
4. the person eating garlic is on the left of the person eating tomato##1
5. the person eating corn is on the right of the person eating peach##1
6. the person eating cherry is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3   |   4    |   5   |   6    |     7      |
| Food   | kiwi | peach | corn | cherry | garlic | tomato | broccoli |

