.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-8::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: time-travel, martial-arts, documentary, action, musical, adventure, superhero
1. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
2. the person watching adventure movies is in the middle##1
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
4. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
5. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3   |   4    |   5    |    6     |   7   |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | martial-arts | time-travel | adventure | action | superhero | documentary |

